sequenceDiagram
  participant Owner as Desktop / VS Code Codex owner
  participant IPC as CodexIpcClient
  participant Feed as CodexIpcFeed
  participant Tracker as ThreadStreamTracker
  participant GW as terminalGateway.js
  participant Android as Android CodexViewModel

  Owner->>IPC: thread-stream-state-changed snapshot/patch
  IPC->>Feed: broadcast message
  Feed->>Tracker: applyBroadcast()
  Tracker-->>Feed: conversation state / projection
  Feed->>Feed: buildDesktopSurfaceSnapshot()
  Feed->>GW: snapshot / event / status
  GW->>Android: codex_ipc_status
  GW->>Android: codex_ipc_conversations
  GW->>Android: codex_ipc_sync_event
  GW->>Android: conversation_surface_snapshot
  GW->>Android: conversation_status_changed
  GW->>Android: conversation_action_required
  Android->>Android: merge snapshot into UI messages / approval / PLAN / goal